3#ifndef __NVKM_FIFO_H__
4#define __NVKM_FIFO_H__
5#include <core/engine.h>
6#include <core/event.h>
7
8#define NVKM_FIFO_CHID_NR 4096
9
10struct nvkm_fifo_engn {
11 struct nvkm_object *object;
12 int refcount;
13 int usecount;
14};
15
16struct nvkm_fifo_chan {
17 const struct nvkm_fifo_chan_func *func;
18 struct nvkm_fifo *fifo;
19 u64 engines;
20 struct nvkm_object object;
21
22 struct list_head head;
23 u16 chid;
24 struct nvkm_gpuobj *inst;
25 struct nvkm_gpuobj *push;
26 struct nvkm_vm *vm;
27#ifdef __NetBSD__
28 bus_space_tag_t bst;
29 bus_space_handle_t bsh;
30 bool mapped;
31 bool subregion;
32#else
33 void __iomem *user;
34#endif
35 u64 addr;
36 u32 size;
37
38 struct nvkm_fifo_engn engn[NVKM_SUBDEV_NR];
39};
40
41struct nvkm_fifo {
42 const struct nvkm_fifo_func *func;
43 struct nvkm_engine engine;
44
45 DECLARE_BITMAP(mask, NVKM_FIFO_CHID_NR);
46 int nr;
47 struct list_head chan;
48 spinlock_t lock;
49
50 struct nvkm_event uevent; /* async user trigger */
51 struct nvkm_event cevent; /* channel creation event */
52};
53
54void nvkm_fifo_pause(struct nvkm_fifo *, unsigned long *);
55void nvkm_fifo_start(struct nvkm_fifo *, unsigned long *);
56
57void nvkm_fifo_chan_put(struct nvkm_fifo *, unsigned long flags,
58 struct nvkm_fifo_chan **);
59struct nvkm_fifo_chan *
60nvkm_fifo_chan_inst(struct nvkm_fifo *, u64 inst, unsigned long *flags);
61struct nvkm_fifo_chan *
62nvkm_fifo_chan_chid(struct nvkm_fifo *, int chid, unsigned long *flags);
63
